Package lusc.net.github

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Defaults
    Defaults coordinates - across the whole of Luscinia - the writing and reading of default parameters for the UI to use.
    Element
    This is the object for elements, the smallest unit of sound measurement in Luscinia.
    Individual
    Individual is the base unit for an individual.
    Luscinia
    This is the main class for the application, and contains the main method entry point.
    Matrix2DOperations
    This class facilitates some matrix functions, especially on spectrograms.
    Song
    Song is the object that recording units are held in.
    SpectrogramMeasurement
    This Class measures elements within spectrograms - measuring a range of acoustic parameters It interacts closely with the Song class.
